    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 3,
    "last_activity_date" : 1358935423,
    "creation_date" : 1358935423,
    "answer_id" : 14476950,
    "question_id" : 957700,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Another solution would be to open the 'run configuration' and then in the 'Environment' tab, set the couple {Path,Value}. </p>\n\n<p>For instance to add a 'lib' directory located at the root of the project,</p>\n\n<pre><code>    Path  &lt;-  ${workspace_loc:name_of_the_project}\\lib\n</code></pre>\n"
