    "last_activity_date" : 1373546303,
    "creation_date" : 1373546303,
    "answer_id" : 17593629,
    "question_id" : 957700,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Sometime we dont get Java Build Path by directly right click on project.\nthen go to properties.... <img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/ewKXd.png\" alt=\"Right Click and go to properties\"></p>\n\n<p>Then Click on java build path<img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/u5gqH.png\" alt=\"Properties Scrren\"></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/HwIOT.png\" alt=\"Click on add external jar\"></p>\n\n<p>Click on tab add external jars and give path of your computer file where u have stored jars.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
